00:07:41.759 --> 00:07:43.000
Tú deseas.

00:07:47.720 --> 00:07:49.000
Qin Moyao.

00:07:49.639 --> 00:07:51.920
Tengo una carta de triunfo.

00:07:53.959 --> 00:07:56.279
